lead_paragraph: Thoroughly embarrassed by Cleveland's record-setting performance, the Atlanta Hawks spent part of Thursday watching film from their Game 2 debacle.

headline.print_headline: Hawks Look for Answers After Getting Embarrassed by Cavs
